title: Villager_Start
---
Villager: Hey there! Nice day
Player: Yeah! What are you up to
Villager: Not much
Player: Nice
Villager: Right?
===

title: Fisherman_Start
---
Fisherman: Hey there, traveler! Beautiful day for fishing, isn't it?
Player: Yeah! Have you caught anything?
Fisherman: Not yet, but I saw something strange in the deep water...
Fisherman: A golden shimmer, like treasure. But it's too deep to reach.
Fisherman: Head east from here. Look for the rock formation shaped like a bird.
Player: Thanks! I'll look for it.
===

title: Gardener_Start
---
Gardener: Oh! Hello! I'm so glad someone's here.
Player: Hi! This garden is beautiful!
Gardener: Thank you! I've been tending it for years.
Gardener: But lately, the flowers on the north side won't bloom.
Gardener: I think they need something special... maybe water from the sacred spring?
Player: Sacred spring? Where's that?
Gardener: High up on the cliff. You'll need to climb to reach it.
Gardener: Be careful up there! And bring me back some spring water if you can.
===

title: Elder_Start
---
Elder: Ah, a visitor. It's been so long since anyone came to this island.
Player: What is this place?
Elder: This island holds many secrets, young one.
Elder: Long ago, it was a sanctuary for birds of all kinds.
Elder: But one by one, they left. Now only a few remain.
Player: Why did they leave?
Elder: The island's magic is fading. The feathers you collect... they're remnants of that magic.
Elder: Gather them all, and perhaps... perhaps the birds will return.
Elder: Look for the highest peak. That's where the last great bird was seen.
===